project_descr:
Expected Outputs are as follows:
1. Bill to monitor and control precursor chemicals
2. Establishment of the Precursor Chemical Unit and all its functions
3.  Policy recommendations developed through capacity development in Complex systems

outputs.output_descr: The Effective Control and Monitoring of Precursor Chemicals in Trinidad and Tobago project seeks to establish a common project management platform for the effective implementation of procedures to  manage and monitor the use of precursor chemicals
donor_name: Ministry of National Security Trinidad and Tobago

project_title: effective control and monitoring of precursor chemicals
